any  member  of  the  volunteer  forces  to  neglect  or  act  in 
conflict with his duty as a member thereof;

(a)  fails without just cause (the proof whereof shall  lie upon 
him) to attend at any time or place lawfully appointed by a 
proper authority for instruction, training or exercise;

(b)  when  in  uniform  or  on  duty  or  undergoing  instruction, 
training or exercise, is drunk or is guilty of insubordinate 
conduct;

